will kill bad guys.

15:29.066 --> 15:31.167
Nope, absolutely not.

15:31.169 --> 15:32.001
No.

15:32.003 --> 15:33.236
Why?

15:33.238 --> 15:34.037
Ugh, okay I got the whites in the

15:34.039 --> 15:34.971
you have to sign this.

15:34.973 --> 15:36.172
I'm not signing anything.

15:36.174 --> 15:38.241
