15:40.044 --> 15:41.978
Now what's going on?

15:41.980 --> 15:43.746
Ask your son.

15:43.748 --> 15:44.580
My son?

15:44.582 --> 15:46.149
Yeah, your son.

15:47.451 --> 15:48.918
Ben?

15:48.920 --> 15:52.655
