16:25.522 --> 16:28.524
Look, I just wanna be there
for my friend, okay?

16:28.526 --> 16:29.625
His dad was killed.

16:29.627 --> 16:31.060
He was fucking murdered.

16:31.062 --> 16:33.396
Watch your mouth.

16:33.398 --> 16:35.031
