16:35.033 --> 16:36.432
'Cause I'm willing to risk my life

16:36.434 --> 16:39.102
Sp Josh doesn't have to grow up with this?

16:39.104 --> 16:40.770
Yeah, I'm a real dirtbag.

16:40.772 --> 16:42.872
No, you're our little boy.

16:42.874 --> 16:45.108
And I'm not gonna bury you, too.

16:45.110 --> 16:47.310
You're 17 years old.

16:47.312 --> 16:48.212
17.

16:49.313 --> 16:52.482
