17:17.008 --> 17:19.608
I mean we love you, buddy.

17:19.611 --> 17:21.077
Right now, you...

17:22.311 --> 17:25.548
but what if somebody else comes home?

17:27.451 --> 17:29.485
I'll be fine.

17:29.487 --> 17:30.319
What?

17:30.321 --> 17:32.622
I need to do this.

17:32.624 --> 17:34.123
I have to be there for him.

17:34.125 --> 17:35.758
I gave him my word.

17:35.760 --> 17:36.726
I know.

17:37.728 --> 17:38.694
I know.

17:41.665 --> 17:43.299
I'm gonna do it.

17:44.334 --> 17:48.838
It's just a matter of
now, or in eight months.

18:01.018 --> 18:01.984
What?

18:04.655 --> 18:07.523
This country is worth defending.

18:07.525 --> 18:09.025
