18:20.437 --> 18:24.307
You know, you have to tell him, okay?

18:24.309 --> 18:27.777
At the very least, you have to tell him.

18:30.647 --> 18:32.281
Alright.

19:12.389 --> 19:14.357
Dedicated it to you.

19:16.727 --> 19:18.361
I ran 2,000 yards.

19:39.449 --> 19:40.416
I'm sorry.

19:56.600 --> 19:57.667
I miss you.

20:33.403 --> 20:35.104
Up in there.

20:35.106 --> 20:36.072
Got this.

21:03.900 --> 21:04.967
Ah, rookie.

21:22.052 --> 21:23.185
Listen, Ben.

21:24.988 --> 21:28.124
I don't like to talk about this, but

21:30.093 --> 21:31.827
when I was drafted,

21:32.963 --> 21:34.363
they put me in a helicopter
and they told me

21:34.365 --> 21:38.167
to shoot anything that
wasn't wearing green.

21:39.670 --> 21:40.636
I did.

21:52.649 --> 21:56.952
To this day, I don't know
why I killed those people.

22:01.024 --> 22:04.160
You need to make your own decisions.

22:06.963 --> 22:08.864
Before you pull the trigger,
you need to be able to

22:08.866 --> 22:11.600
look yourself in the mirror,

22:11.602 --> 22:14.070
and say why you're doin' it.

22:15.572 --> 22:17.940
And that you believe in it.

22:51.074 --> 22:53.843
It's fucking weird, not
playing this season.

22:53.845 --> 22:56.746
Yeah, it's bullshit, coach
won't let you play.

22:56.748 --> 22:57.713
Nah.

22:58.815 --> 23:00.349
I understand.

23:00.351 --> 23:03.018
I mean, I'm not gonna be here
for half the games anyway.

23:03.020 --> 23:04.453
Wrong of me to even try out like that.

23:04.455 --> 23:05.688
Yeah, why didn't you wait

23:05.690 --> 23:08.190
