23:08.192 --> 23:09.558
I don't know.

23:10.560 --> 23:13.496
I guess I just didn't think about it.

23:13.498 --> 23:15.030
But in the scheme of things,
what's more important?

23:15.032 --> 23:18.534
Couple high school basketball
games, or the war?

23:18.536 --> 23:20.903
