Easy decision, bro.

23:22.073 --> 23:23.372
Easy decision.

23:27.344 --> 23:31.647
Your mom still bein' a bitch
about that paperwork?

23:33.650 --> 23:35.851
Man, I'm right behind you.

23:35.853 --> 23:38.220
