and for that, I'm sorry.

01:30:19.386 --> 01:30:21.787
That is my greatest regret.

01:30:23.322 --> 01:30:24.856
If I could have that moment back,

01:30:24.858 --> 01:30:27.492
I would do it so differently.

01:30:27.494 --> 01:30:32.063
But I don't regret not getting
pulled into that bullshit.

01:30:32.065 --> 01:30:33.198
And you think I do?

01:30:33.200 --> 01:30:34.699
You should!

01:30:34.701 --> 01:30:36.435
You are fucking something else.

01:30:36.437 --> 01:30:38.437
What did you expect?

01:30:38.439 --> 01:30:40.772
That I was gonna worship you and
thank you for your service?

01:30:40.774 --> 01:30:41.740
I never asked for that.

01:30:41.742 --> 01:30:42.808
Huh, does that piss you off?

01:30:42.810 --> 01:30:44.242
That I don't shake your hand,

01:30:44.244 --> 01:30:45.777
and thank you for
everything you sacrificed?

01:30:45.779 --> 01:30:47.379
You got the freedom to say
whatever the fuck you want!

01:30:47.381 --> 01:30:49.815
Cut the canned bullshit, man!

01:30:49.817 --> 01:30:50.649
I know you!

01:30:50.651 --> 01:30:51.616
You don't know me.

01:30:51.618 --> 01:30:52.584
I know it pisses you off!

01:30:52.586 --> 01:30:53.718
I can see it in your eyes.

01:30:53.720 --> 01:30:55.253
I'm an ungrateful fuck.

01:30:55.255 --> 01:30:57.556
Sorry if I didn't want to get
dragged into that bullshit.

01:30:57.558 --> 01:31:00.025
Why don't you tell my dead friends that?

01:31:00.027 --> 01:31:01.460
You volunteered!

01:31:01.462 --> 01:31:03.595
You signed your name down
on a piece of paper!

01:31:03.597 --> 01:31:05.864
At what point do you become
a willing participant

01:31:05.866 --> 01:31:07.466
in something that you know is wrong?

01:31:07.468 --> 01:31:09.301
By the time I re-upped, do you really think

01:31:09.303 --> 01:31:12.571
I gave a shit about why we were there?

01:31:12.573 --> 01:31:15.407
I wanted to make sure
that the 17 year old kid

01:31:15.409 --> 01:31:18.043
with a 90 IQ, the guy who joined

01:31:18.045 --> 01:31:20.479
because he wanted to protect his country

01:31:20.481 --> 01:31:23.748
got to come back home to his mom and dad.

01:31:23.750 --> 01:31:25.817
And if I didn't go, somewhat who wasn't

01:31:25.819 --> 01:31:27.285
as good as me, would've.

01:31:27.287 --> 01:31:28.753
That doesn't justify this killing!

01:31:28.755 --> 01:31:31.256
Do you realize how fucking
ridiculous that sounds!

01:31:31.258 --> 01:31:33.091
Soldiers go where you ask us to go!

01:31:33.093 --> 01:31:35.927
We are a tool, a concept
you refuse to understand!

01:31:35.929 --> 01:31:36.995
I understand it!

01:31:36.997 --> 01:31:38.263
Do you?

01:31:38.265 --> 01:31:39.498
Or do you just like refuse to process...

01:31:39.500 --> 01:31:40.732
awful easy to say coming from the safety

01:31:40.734 --> 01:31:42.367
of your suburban home, where people

01:31:42.369 --> 01:31:43.668
aren't killing your friends!

01:31:43.670 --> 01:31:45.036
It's not that simple!

01:31:45.038 --> 01:31:46.505
You put yourself in the situation

01:31:46.507 --> 01:31:48.173
where you had to kill somebody

01:31:48.175 --> 01:31:49.908
for something you didn't even believe in!

01:31:49.910 --> 01:31:51.510
I couldn't do that!

01:31:51.512 --> 01:31:53.612
Yeah, I would have trouble
sleeping at night, too.

01:32:05.324 --> 01:32:06.358
You done?

01:32:28.915 --> 01:32:29.848
Enough Ben!

01:32:29.850 --> 01:32:30.582
I don't want to hurt you!

01:32:56.075 --> 01:32:57.042
Fucker.

01:33:01.414 --> 01:33:03.281
I'll fucking kill you.

01:33:47.660 --> 01:33:51.563
You're a scrappy mother fucker, aren't you?

01:33:55.234 --> 01:33:57.168
I was fighting for my life.

01:35:13.713 --> 01:35:15.780
When I was over there

01:35:17.983 --> 01:35:20.285
I kept turning on the news

01:35:21.954 --> 01:35:24.923
expecting to see people protesting

01:35:25.958 --> 01:35:28.693
trying to bring us home, you know?

01:35:30.296 --> 01:35:32.097
You know what I saw?

01:35:33.532 --> 01:35:36.167
Survivor, fucking Kardashians.

01:35:43.476 --> 01:35:46.444
Did you once try to bring me home?

01:35:47.446 --> 01:35:48.646
Man, I can't sleep at night,

01:35:48.648 --> 01:35:51.850
and I probably never really will.

01:35:51.852 --> 01:35:53.318
While the rest of the country curls up

01:35:53.320 --> 01:35:55.353
in their Egyptian cotton sheets,

01:35:55.355 --> 01:35:57.255
and their cozy, gas-heated homes.

01:35:57.257 --> 01:36:00.892
And they get to dream
about fucking sugarplums.

01:36:00.894 --> 01:36:04.629
The price of our way of life is not shared.

01:36:05.598 --> 01:36:07.565
I know I'm not a hero.

01:36:09.435 --> 01:36:11.936
No sane person comes back
from that fucked-up nightmare

01:36:11.938 --> 01:36:14.472
proud of everything they did.

01:36:14.474 --> 01:36:17.242
All I could do was one thing,

01:36:17.244 --> 01:36:19.878
and that's keep my guys alive.

01:36:22.381 --> 01:36:23.348
And I did.

01:36:36.095 --> 01:36:37.395
So what now?

01:36:56.949 --> 01:36:57.916
Oh fuck.

01:37:03.789 --> 01:37:06.424
Still feels like it's there.

01:37:08.527 --> 01:37:10.495
IUD got us in a hum-v.

01:37:10.497 --> 01:37:14.132
It was fucking.

01:37:15.568 --> 01:37:19.504
Worst part is, I swear I have
a huge blister on my big toe!

01:37:19.506 --> 01:37:22.407
But when I looked down, nothing.

01:37:22.409 --> 01:37:23.908
No foot, no shin!

01:37:23.910 --> 01:37:26.544
My whole god damn leg is gone!

01:37:31.150 --> 01:37:34.085
I had the coolest fucking
tattoo on my calf.

01:37:34.087 --> 01:37:36.020
400 bucks fucking wasted.

01:37:36.022 --> 01:37:40.325
That shit pissed me off.

01:37:42.228 --> 01:37:44.529
So, so go to colleges.

01:37:44.531 --> 01:37:45.530
I mean tell your story.

01:37:45.532 --> 01:37:47.498
Call out the hypocrites.

01:37:47.500 --> 01:37:48.666
Come on, Benson.

01:37:48.668 --> 01:37:50.034
A room full of teenagers and listen to them

01:37:50.036 --> 01:37:53.504
talk about shit they know nothing about?

01:37:54.607 --> 01:37:55.874
No thanks.

01:37:55.876 --> 01:37:57.342
These kids were four when 9/11 happened.

01:37:57.344 --> 01:38:01.212
It's about as meaningful as
saying Pearl harbor, to them.

01:38:15.361 --> 01:38:18.563
If you're not gonna tell
them, then who will?

01:38:18.565 --> 01:38:20.965
I'm the enemy, man.

01:38:20.967 --> 01:38:22.433
I'm the machine.

01:38:23.736 --> 01:38:27.605
They'll never hear me even
if I did say something.

01:38:32.878 --> 01:38:36.014
But you know what I would tell them?

01:38:37.416 --> 01:38:39.117
That it's criminal.

01:38:41.287 --> 01:38:43.187
That hero shit.

01:38:43.189 --> 01:38:47.225
When a life gets snuffed
out like it's nothing.

01:38:50.029 --> 01:38:51.296
Imagine growing up so poor

01:38:51.298 --> 01:38:54.098
where your only chance for a better life

01:38:54.100 --> 01:38:56.834
requires you to gamble with it.

01:38:58.470 --> 01:39:00.171
And for what?

01:39:00.173 --> 01:39:02.373
Free college tuition, or
to protect their country?

01:39:02.375 --> 01:39:03.841
Which one is it?

01:39:04.576 --> 01:39:07.378
That is what's fucking criminal.

01:39:10.883 --> 01:39:13.851
They don't want to be heroes, man.

01:39:15.054 --> 01:39:17.455
They just want a chance.

01:39:17.457 --> 01:39:19.257
They want adventure.

01:39:20.259 --> 01:39:21.960
Wars destroy lives.

01:39:24.129 --> 01:39:26.097
It shreds friendships.

01:39:27.166 --> 01:39:30.568
It's not cool, it's not bad-ass,

01:39:30.570 --> 01:39:34.138
there's no fast cars, no hot chicks.

01:39:34.140 --> 01:39:36.841
And all the heroes fucking die.

01:39:39.545 --> 01:39:42.680
But you know what I wonder the most?

01:39:44.483 --> 01:39:46.484
Is who I would've been.

01:40:38.904 --> 01:40:41.439
You feel good about yourself?

01:40:43.442 --> 01:40:44.809
You beat up a cripple.

01:40:46.613 --> 01:40:48.346
A god damn amputee!

01:40:55.254 --> 01:40:56.921
Hey, you remember that time

01:40:56.923 --> 01:40:58.423
we drove up here with your dad?

01:40:58.425 --> 01:40:59.390
In the back of the pick-up?

01:40:59.392 --> 01:41:00.925
Dude, those puddles were huge!

01:41:00.927 --> 01:41:02.427
Downright dangerous.

01:41:02.429 --> 01:41:03.761
We could've been killed
before our balls dropped.

01:41:03.763 --> 01:41:05.530
Yeah, I'm surprised they did that.

01:41:05.532 --> 01:41:06.998
You know, you weren't the only one.

01:41:07.000 --> 01:41:09.534
We were all very concerned about
those lopsided little guys.

01:41:09.536 --> 01:41:10.568
Whatever came of the left one?

01:41:10.570 --> 01:41:11.736
Oh, it's still crooked,

01:41:11.738 --> 01:41:12.937
and way higher than the other one.

01:41:12.939 --> 01:41:14.238
Can you still pull it up inside your body?

01:41:14.240 --> 01:41:15.106
Hell yeah, man!

01:41:17.143 --> 01:41:18.476
Oh, fuck.

01:41:18.478 --> 01:41:20.845
Jesus, what happened to your face?

01:41:20.847 --> 01:41:22.914
What's wrong with my face?

01:41:24.184 --> 01:41:25.116
No seriously, what's wrong with my face?

01:41:25.118 --> 01:41:26.751
It looks better than before.

01:41:45.204 --> 01:41:49.307
Does anybody even pick
up hitchhikers anymore?

01:41:49.309 --> 01:41:52.743
Rapists and murderers, I think.

01:41:52.745 --> 01:41:53.578
Perfect.

01:42:31.484 --> 01:42:32.683
Just in case.

